"Special Commemorative Page of Kim Jong Il" Opens 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 27 (KCNA) -- The U.S. Group for the Study of the Songun Politics opened Internet homepage "Special commemorative page of Kim Jong Il" on February 14 on the occasion of the February holiday.
 Edited in the homepage are the full text of leader Kim Jong Il's famous work "Abuses of Socialism Are Intolerable," propositions from his work "Let Us March Forward Dynamically along the Road of Socialism and Communism under the Unfurled Banner of the Anti-imperialist Struggle" and the full text of the book "Songun Politics of General Kim Jong Il". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Also carried in the homepage is an article of Jo Il Min, chief of the Pyongyang Mission of the National Democratic Front of South Korea, titled "Why do we worship and uphold General Kim Jong Il". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The article said: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il is a great thinker and theoretician, a great statesman, a great man and the sun of the 21st century. His thought, statesmanship and achievements, all of them reach the acme of charm. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Anyone cannot but be captivated by his greatness as an outstanding thinker and theoretician when recollecting a few facts such as the programme of modeling the whole society on the Juche idea, the idea and theory on global independence, the socialist idea and theory of the present times and the idea and theory on the Songun politics. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He incapacitated the strong-arm action of the U.S. imperialists with the might of ideology and Songun, the strength of single-hearted unity, defended the dignity and sovereignty of the country and the nation and performed noteworthy exploits in ensuring peace and stability in the Korean peninsula.  He is the lodestar of national reunification and the great incarnation of benevolence. He defends and flowers today and tomorrow of fellow countrymen with his Songun politics. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The absolute faith that the great leader of the Korean nation is the only one, General Kim Jong Il, is cherished in the hearts of all the people. The victory of the cause of the NDFSK which worships and upholds him is sure to come.

Meeting of Presidium of North Headquarters of Pomminryon Held 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 27 (KCNA) -- A meeting of the Presidium of the North Headquarters of the National Alliance for the Country's Reunification (Pomminryon) was held at the People's Palace of Culture yesterday.
 Present at the meeting were members of the Presidium of the North Headquarters of Pomminryon and members of its Central Committee. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The meeting discussed its agenda item "On thoroughly implementing the tasks for national reunification set forth in the joint editorial of this year and at the joint meeting of the government, political parties and organizations of the DPRK". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 An Kyong Ho, chairman of the North Headquarters of Pomminryon, made a report which was followed by speeches. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The meeting recalled that the North Headquarters of Pomminryon intensified the work with the organizations of all social standings in the south and overseas and conducted a vigorous movement for national reunification last year after fixing it as a "year of defending independence and peace through national cooperation". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The meeting called for paving a wide avenue for independent reunification through national cooperation under the uplifted banner of our nation-first spirit as required by the present situation, taking note of the situation in the country which has become tenser due to the U.S. and reactionaries at home and abroad, its followers. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting that the anti-U.S. struggle is a life and death struggle decisive of the dignity and destiny of the Korean nation, the meeting called on all the Korean people to make an active contribution to building the structure of the Korean nation's confrontation with the U.S. through practical actions. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It underlined the need to steadily improve the work of Pomminryon in keeping with the situation prevailing in Korea after the publication of the June 15 North-South Joint Declaration and intensify the struggle to realize the legalization of the South Headquarters of Pomminryon and the South Korean Federation of University Student Councils. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A resolution was adopted at the meeting.

Rally Held to Mark 9th Anniversary of Pomminryon South Headquarters 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 27 (KCNA) -- A rally was held at Hanyang University of south Korea on February 22 to mark the 9th anniversary of the South Headquarters of the National Alliance for the Country's Reunification (Pomminryon).
 At the rally Chairman Ra Chang Sun of Pomminryon South Headquarters made an address and prominent figures of various organisations congratulatory speeches. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They said Pomminryon has all along worked hard for the great national unity and national reunification. They stressed the need to wage a vigorous struggle to pave a broad avenue for the reunification of the country through national cooperation under the banner of our nation-first spirit. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 An "appeal to the people" was made public at the Second Meeting of the 8th Central Committee of Pomminryon South Headquarters held prior to the rally. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The appeal said now the Korean nation is exposed to a grave threat from war moves of the U.S. But there are a strong war deterrent built up to cope with the U.S. moves to provoke a war on the Korean peninsula in the north and the people standing firm against the U.S. in the south, it noted. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It went on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The June 15 joint declaration is a yardstick distinguishing patriotism from treachery. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 National cooperation is the only way of putting into reality the structure of the Korean nation vs. U.S. confrontation by practical actions and realizing the desire of the nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It called for smashing the U.S. war moves getting all the more pronounced and winning in the confrontation with the U.S., the sworn enemy, without fail.

Inter-Korean Working Contacts Held 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kaesong, February 26 (KCNA) -- The 9th north-south working contact for reconnecting the rail and road links and the 4th north-south working contact for cooperation on marine transportation were made in Kaesong from February 25 to 26.
 At the contact for reconnecting the rail and road links between the north and the south both sides adopted an agreement after discussing a timetable for technical service for the repair and servicing of equipment for undertaking the projects of reconnecting the rail and road links, a timetable for the provision and construction of an asphalt complex, a timetable for the provision of the equipment and materials yet to be delivered for the projects and other matters. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It was decided to agree on the basic agreement on the setting up of a truck service office and its operation and the provision of train service at the fourth meeting of the panel for reconnecting the rail and road links between the north and the south. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 At the working contact for cooperation on marine transportation both sides had a discussion on the date of effectuating the agreement on marine transportation between the north and the south that had already been adopted and an appendix for its implementation and published a joint press release stating that they would adopt the appendix at an early date after finalizing it by way of exchanging documents. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They agreed to fix the date and venue for the 5th north-south working contact for cooperation in marine transportation after discussing it by way of exchanging documents.

Foreigners Visit DPRK Embassies 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 27 (KCNA) -- The vice minister of Land and Cooperatives Development of Malaysia who is vice-chairman of the Malaysian People's Movement and the vice minister of Youth and Sports of Malaysia separately paid congratulatory visits to the DPRK embassy in that country on Feb. 16 on the occasion of the birthday of leader Kim Jong Il.
 They laid floral baskets before the portraits of President Kim Il Sung and Kim Jong Il and paid their respects to them. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They handed to the DPRK ambassador messages of greetings to Kim Jong Il. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The vice minister of Land and Cooperatives Development of Malaysia expressed belief that the good friendly relations between the Workers' Party of Korea and the MPM would grow stronger, showing the willingness to make every possible effort to this end. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 On Feb. 15 the vice-chairman of the National Democratic Party of Egypt who is deputy prime minister and minister of Agriculture and Land Reclamation, the chairman of the National Progressive Unionist Party of Egypt, the chairman of the Egypt-Korea Friendship Association, the chairman of the Egyptian Committee for the Study of the Juche Idea and other prominent figures of different circles paid congratulatory visits to the DPRK embassy in Cairo and laid floral baskets before a photograph of Kim Il Sung and Kim Jong Il standing together on Mt. Paektu. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Meanwhile, the coordinator (leader) of the National Executive Committee of the Workers' Party of Mexico, the deputy general secretary of the Syria's Baath Arab Socialist Party, the defense and foreign ministers of Laos, the general secretary of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of India (Marxist), the commander-in-chief and the director of the General Information Department of the Malaysian Army, the presidency of Indonesia, the Mexico-Korea Friendship Association, and governments, political parties, organizations and prominent figures of different countries sent floral baskets and messages of greetings to DPRK missions on the occasion of the February holiday.

Japan Should Not Be Allowed to Repeat Its History of Aggression of Korea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 27 (KCNA) -- Japan should never be allowed to repeat the history of the Japanese imperialist aggression of Korea, says Rodong Sinmun Friday in a signed article.
 The article goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Japanese aggressors fabricated the "Kanghwa Island Treaty" 128 years ago. It was the first treaty imposed upon Korea by Japan whereby it infringed upon the sovereignty of the Korean nation by military threat and blackmail in a bid to invade Korea and put it under its control and it was the first product of the collusion between the U.S. and Japanese aggressors for the invasion of Korea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The article cites facts to prove that the Japanese aggressors deeply infiltrated into the political, economic, cultural and other fields of Korea on the strength of the treaty and finally occupied it by force of arms, thus forcing the Korean people to suffer untold misfortune, pain and disasters for more than 40 years. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Japan is obliged to redeem its crime-woven past and apologize for all the crimes it committed against the Korean people in the past and compensate for them. However, it is whitewashing and justifying them in a bid to realize its ambition to reinvade Korea. It is clearly evidenced by the facts that the Japanese authorities are persistently pursuing their hostile policy toward the DPRK, evading their responsibility for liquidating Japan's past, the core issue of the DPRK-Japan Pyongyang Declaration, paid visits to the "Yasukuni Shrine" from the outset of the year, adopted a legislation to apply economic sanctions against the DPRK, pursuant to the U.S. offensive to destroy the DPRK with nukes, and made a territorial claim to Tok Islet, etc. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  The Japanese reactionaries are gravely mistaken, however. The Korean people are not what they used to be in the past. If the Japanese reactionaries launch the reinvasion of Korea, they will meet nothing but a miserable destruction.

Military Attaches Visit Ski Training Centre
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 27 (KCNA) -- Members of the military attaches' corps here on Feb. 26 went round the all-round ski training centre built by the Korean People's Army
 The training centre built in the district of North Phothae Mountain of Mt. Paektu area, the holy land of revolution, is splendid in scale and facilities which are suitable for ski training and races and all kinds of amusement games. It is another creation of the Songun era. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 There are several ski courses and cableways in the training center. It is fully equipped with modern facilities and apparatus necessary for ski training such as snow tamping cars, snow buses, snow motorcycles and snow sleighs. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Before watching soldiers undergoing ski training the visitors were briefed on the training center in front of the monument to the on-the-spot guidance of leader Kim Jong Il erected there. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The soldiers well displayed the militant spirit of the Korean People's Army by performing a number of training events requiring boldness, braveness, refined physical preparedness and patience. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The visitors went up by snow bus to the top of the North Phothae Mountain where Mt. Paektu is visible and enjoyed a bird's-eye view of its area. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 And they spent a joyful time of rest by sliding on skis, snow motorcycles and snow sleighs. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 After going round the training center, military attaches said the combat strength of the Korean People's Army was growing immensely stronger as its soldiers were training themselves for battles in such wonderful training center under deep care and solicitude of Supreme Commander Kim Jong Il.

Meeting of Ideological Workers Closes
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, February 27 (KCNA) -- The meeting of ideological workers of the Workers' Party of Korea closed today after successfully winding up its work.
 Jong Ha Chol, secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea, made a report titled "Let Us Fully Demonstrate the Might of the Ideological Work of Our Party under the Great Songun Banner!" which was followed by speeches. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The reporter said that leader Kim Jong Il with clairvoyant and rare wisdom set out the principle of Juche that idea decides everything and considered ideology as the most efficient weapon for a revolutionary party. He attached primary importance to the ideological work of the Party from the early days of his guidance over the WPK and has wisely led it for the last four decades, he added, and continued: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il formulated President Kim Il Sung's revolutionary idea as an idea guiding our times at a time when the Korean revolution entered a historic turning-point and ushered in a new era for the development of the ideological work by proclaiming the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea on that basis. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 This occupies a most brilliant page in his history of leadership over the party ideological work. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He has consistently maintained the leadership principle of putting the ideological work above all other work throughout the history of the Korean revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 His wise leadership over the party ideological work finds its vivid manifestation in the fact that he set a fine example of the party political work in the Songun era and made sure that it was followed by all party organizations. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The single-hearted unity of the whole Party and all the people around the leader, the only central figure, has become stronger than ever before and the ideological position of socialism in the DPRK has been remarkably consolidated. This is the greatest achievement made in the Party ideological work. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The party ideological education has been steadily intensified to meet the requirements of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea. As a result, the leader, the Party, the army and the people have achieved perfect unity and cohesion and they have formed indestructible ranks of Songun revolutionary comrades armed with the spirit of devotedly defending the leader in the Songun era. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The major task before the party ideological workers at present is to strengthen in every way the driving force of the Songun revolution and arouse the whole Party and army and all the people to a struggle to defend socialism and to the building of a great prosperous powerful nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 All the party organizations and ideological workers should help all the party members and other working people repose absolute trust in Kim Jong Il and devotedly defend him and display intense loyalty and creative enthusiasm in their efforts to accomplish the noble cause of modeling the whole Party and the society on the Songun idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The reporter called upon all the party ideological workers to creditably discharge their historic mission they have assumed before the Party, the leader, the motherland and the people, highly honored to be ideological workers in Kim Jong Il's glorious era. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The speakers said that great changes have been effected in all fields of the ideological work in the course of embodying  Kim Jong Il's Juche-oriented theory of ideological work. All the achievements made in the party ideological work are a precious fruition of his judicious and tested revolutionary leadership and a clear proof of the validity and the tremendous vitality of the programme for modeling the whole society on the Juche idea, they added. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They evinced their pledge to successfully implement tasks set forth in the congratulatory message sent by the WPK Central Committee, bearing deep in mind the high awareness and responsibility of taking charge of the Party's ideological front.
